            "title": "How We Make A Difference",
            "title_size": "h2",
            "text": "<h6>COMMUNITY-FOCUSED AND FAMILY-MINDED</h6><p>We care about who makes our pieces, just as much as who they are made for. Our people are the beating heart of our brand, so we put them first. We are passionate about supporting local communities and creating a caring and collaborative work environment for everybody.</p>",
