          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "pre_title": "",
            "title": "We Ensure",
            "title_size": "h2",
            "text": "<h6>EMPLOYEE BENEFITS</h6><p>All head office and design studio employees in Australia and Indonesia are paid above the national minimum wage along with additional benefits. We also provide a safe and supportive working environment for all employees.</p><h6>UPSKILLING AND TRAINING</h6><p>We provide training programs both externally and internally for individuals who may not have extensive experience or skills prior to their role at FAITHFULL but are eager to learn and develop their repertoire. We offer access to both professional education and a range of holistic courses.</p><h6>COMMUNITY INVESTMENT</h6><p>Since the beginning, we have provided financial and managerial assistance to local businesses and communities to support their growth in conjunction with our own. As FAITHFULL continues to grow, our ongoing goal is to see these small, independent partners and factories and the people within them prosper even further.</p><p><strong>PARENTAL SUPPORT</strong></p><p>We support all parents returning to the workforce after their parental leave by employing home industry contractors. Many members of our design office work from home, allowing them the freedom and duality to support their families.</p>",
